Fake news detector

description:
we will use kaggle for dataset https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/clmentbisaillon/fake-and-real-news-dataset
short project implementation guidelines:
i.  The above dataset contains two files true.csv and false.csv
ii. The data premise title,text,subject,date.so we will create a model which will be trained on these two datasets
iii.We will ckeanup the stopwords from the text. we will also use stemming
iv. We will create a model fake_news_model.pkl
v.  Using this model we will classify any news whether this is fake or not.
vi. We will use train test split on above two csv files to train our model best.
vii.We may extend this one a streamlit app where we will enter any news text and the model should give the answer whether it is fake or not using confidance score


Follow the below structure

fake-news-detector/
│
├── data/
│   └── True.csv, False.csv
│
├── model/
│   └── fake_news_model.pkl
│
├── train.py
├── app.py
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md